{"tid":1722967,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰略問題］打陣地戰我地輸撚梗！要返去打游擊！","createTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:27:10.000Z","uid":303932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cb33433eeb6c39108c9452152b37f192683e5539","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"我都係中大人，見到咁齊心守中大當然好感動。亦見到國際社會幫手撳停，進攻大學係國際大忌。<br />\n但過咗最緊張時刻，開始感覺氣氛似曾相識，好似五年前嘅雨傘：<br />\n- 佔領區內一切都好美好<br />\n- 封咗主幹道要求政府讓步<br />\n- （經中間人）談判，然後政府虛應<br />\n- 佔領地要人守，日日都喺度，又成日要擔心幾時被狗攻，出現疲態<br />\n- 無晒方向，慢慢開始有人沉醉於佔領區既美好，同時開始有人心急，於是開始分化<br />\n- 然後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家知唔知點解哩場香港保衛戰可以打咁耐？</span><br />\n因為：<br />\n- 我哋兵無常態，甚至無人知聽日示威會喺邊度！<br />\n- 我哋有得返去充電！<br />\n- 政府都唔知去邊度搵你，連談判虛應都無機會！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋今次能夠持續，除咗不割席不分化不篤灰，仲因為係游擊戰，唔係陣地戰！唔會死守，HIT AND RUN!!!</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今個星期既然各大學都提早完sem，亦發展出不同時間（黎明、lunch、晚間）不同地點突襲或集會，各大學實在不宜死守，等各大學勇武可以繼續全港游擊纏繞戰，否則有機會被狗一網打盡，因為要搵你而家實在太容易！</span><br />\n<br />\n你跟住會問，唔守咁班狗入來大學點算？<br />\n如果所有勇武、文具同魔法都走晒，D狗照入大學，甚至搜查大學、進駐大學，咁就反而係發爛反攻嘅機會！<br />\n和勇都可以反攻，國際可以發爛，我方出師有名。<br />\n就係要狗有陣地，又唔知幾時被人攻，點攻法！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陣地戰，被動等被人攻，壓力大，消耗大，係輸撚梗！<br />\n游擊戰，主動決定幾時攻，攻邊度，咁先有以弱勝強！<br />\n越南就係咁打贏美軍！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，分享梁天琦嘅一句話，同勇武義士共勉：<br />\n<br />\n當本應解決社會問題的人選擇冷待，反而熱衷於將香港的命運放上賭桌作政治豪賭，我們需要的，不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭，而是在苦難中煉成堅毅與盼望。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c1906dc2ab245e0d515c0ea8a0546544502207b8","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"自推10下!!"},{"pid":"e4693f55d4e7143639f46a9b0502031ca4346f32","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:08:43.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"5dc3b9d3f101f6c0557b76d33eca072f2a4e52fd","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"96f2434749c2a860c52268a01abab42ef2d6284e","tid":1722967,"uid":324954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca283676770b05dcaad11548d64c88492591f76a","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"bb458c4050714d340eebab6178ea8bc283d41b93","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"878477b295f78ac3360b772739c150988d4381c1","tid":1722967,"uid":275006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:17:31.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e53562b5dc1ae3fdc1a8f40044e8d8037e65dd07","tid":1722967,"uid":275006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:17:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06b7d6284714c9b8cda334c7e19ef0dee6cbed63","tid":1722967,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"fd61520b8b617872c8d0d46e23be2333d